Ah, but for those with U-pipes, there's a ready source of heat BEFORE
the heat exhangers- Prepare burger a la
http://home.austin.rr.com/rajordan/high-country/manifold.html and wire
wrap it into the bend of the UPIPE.  I suppose a mini-oven with a door
could be fabricated over it (-8

